# DATABASE WORKFLOW RULES

## Rule DB.0: Environment Selection

**ALWAYS use the EXACT environment the user requests.**

| Environment | MCP Server | Host | Port | User | Database |
|-------------|-----------|------|------|------|----------|
| Dev | user-postgres (Dev) | 10.236.20.21 | 5432 | postgres | phoenix |
| Dev2 | user-postgres (Dev2) | 10.236.20.22 | 5432 | postgres | phoenix |
| Test | user-postgres (Test) | 10.236.20.24 | 5432 | postgres | phoenix |
